# ### 💬 COMMENTS ------------------------

### Add Comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "issue": "69c040d7d0c15831bad5b175",
  "content": "I will fix this bug"
}


### Get Comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/issue/69c040d7d0c15831bad5b175

### Get Comments of PR
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/pr/69bed167588a759f2fdde520

### Get Comment
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/id/69c04152d0c15831bad5b18f


### Update Comment
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/comments/69c04152d0c15831bad5b18f
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated comment"
}


### Delete Comment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/69c04152d0c15831bad5b18f